    </figure>
    <figure id="fig-00002" class="scaled-down">
    <title/>
    <media alt="Part d shows Insert selected from the menu. This is listed in the open window: Column left, Column right, Chart, Image, and Drawing. Part e shows a new column created to the right of Column B with cell C1 having the same blue formatting as the other cells in that row. All of the columns to the right are now shifted right. Part f shows Column C filled with data.">
